WEBVTT

00:01.569 --> 00:04.738
♪♪

00:04.772 --> 00:08.076
Dan Halen: Welcome, everyone,
to the recently renamed

00:08.109 --> 00:10.744
Winter Solstice Festival.

00:10.778 --> 00:12.146
In an effort to celebrate

00:12.180 --> 00:14.248
