will now be called

00:20.288 --> 00:24.358
The Evergreen
of Seasonal Inclusiveness!

00:24.392 --> 00:25.693
[ Light applause, whistling ]

00:25.726 --> 00:28.262
We added one of these
candleholders here

00:28.296 --> 00:30.364
to celebrate the Jews
or something.

00:30.398 --> 00:31.699
I think it's called
a menorah.

00:31.732 --> 00:34.102
I think it's called
"Who told you to speak"?

00:34.135 --> 00:37.171
Kwanzites, we give you
a half-hearted nod

00:37.205 --> 00:39.440
