of Neil deGrasse Tyson

00:57.758 --> 01:00.528
staring at aliens
and black holes, whatever.

01:00.561 --> 01:02.530
And finally,
to top the tree,

01:02.563 --> 01:05.366
the traditional,
non-denominational

01:05.399 --> 01:08.202
glitter-sphere
of ambiguity.

01:08.236 --> 01:10.871
Have a very merry,
gender-neutral,

01:10.904 --> 01:13.607
winter-based
period of time.

01:13.641 --> 01:15.543
[ Electricity buzzes ]
[ Cheers and applause ]

01:15.576 --> 01:17.211
